  "text": "Alternatively, one can use feature-based methods such as SIFT [CITATION_1] , or its variant ASIFT [CITATION_2] which is designed to be fully affine invariant. Similarly, [CITATION_3] provide a fast image matching method, based on a kernel projection scheme for matching detected interest points between images.",
